{
 "name": "RPlog_Paving_a_Road_to_Hell",
 "title": "Paving a Road to Hell",
 "summary": "Aboard a ship, the cheerful Amylynn checks in on Paul Nighman, who pores over a book and computer terminal while the young Shenner dozes in a heap of pillows and blankets nearby. Over the course of a long, quiet stretch, the small found-family of travelers -- Paul, Shenner, and others including Jessalyn, Luke, Lando, and Lelila -- pass the time amid the cargo, books, and instruments of their cramped quarters. The unhurried scene of rest, banter, and gentle companionship belies the darker road the title hints lies ahead, closing on Paul settling Shenner down to sleep before turning in himself.",
